+
+**Standing constraint on all items:** preserve **data, DQ, features, usability, institutional-grade++**. Additive, audited, test-backed, deterministic; no production/VPS mutation during gate freezes.
+
+---
+
+## DONE on branch `cursor/trd-089-latency-telemetry-8e88`
+
+| Commit | What | Inst++ value |
+|--------|------|--------------|
+| TRD-089 | Tick-to-trade telemetry wired into the live execution hot path (T₀ scan → T₂ ack); shadow stays 0 | Latency is now *measurable in production* (Stage-3 enabler) |
+| evidence engine | `evidence_stats.py` (seeded bootstrap ROI CI, Wilson proportion CI, significance grading) + wired into `gate_profile_compare` | A profile is `sufficient`/`promotable` only when ROI CI lower bound clears 0 **and** beats baseline — kills thin-sample false positives |
