+| players fix | merged duplicate `{% block extra_js %}` in `players.html` | Restores a 500-ing dashboard page + greens CI |
+| docs | `PROP_DESK_STRATEGY.md`, `TRADING_REPO_EXTRACTION_PLAN.md`, this file | Direction + executable handoffs |
+
+> Push is blocked only on credentials (agent token scoped to `football-app`). Rebase note + patch in `TRADING_REPO_EXTRACTION_PLAN.md` §1.
+
+---
+
+## QUEUE — next, in priority order
+
+### Q1. Make significance the promotion gate everywhere (extends Tier 0)
+- Surface `roi_ci_low_pct` / `roi_significant_positive` / `clv_beat_close` on `/performance` and `/status#audit-evidence` (UI already reads `/api/health`).
+- Add a **bootstrap CI to the CLI** `pred-log-backtest` / `value_replay.replay_report_dict` output (currently point ROI only).
+- Gate the deploy scripts: `apply-vps-*` should refuse to run unless the latest `comparison_gate_profiles.json` shows a `promotable` profile on the forward cohort.
