+### Q2. Automate evidence growth (the actual Stage-1 unblock)
+- Cron `scripts/run_forward_backfill_plan.sh` daily; track `audit_odds_capture.capture_rate_pct` and `clv_beat_close` as monitored time series (target: forward 1X2 capture ≥50% 7d, CLV n≥25 with Wilson low > 50%).
