+- Schedule chaos/disconnect/SIGKILL-recovery tests as recurring **live game-days**; wire `trading_slo_*` to Grafana alerts.
+
+### Q5. Repo separation (`hibs-trading`)
+- Execute `TRADING_REPO_EXTRACTION_PLAN.md` after 2026-06-18. Independent CI, secrets, blast radius.
+
+### Q6. CI hardening into a gate
+- Phase-3 gate + full `pytest` + evidence-grade check must **block merge**.
+- Add property-based tests on money paths (risk kernel, settlement `_settled`, odds-thin line-shop fill).
+
+### Q7. Stage-2 statistical arbitrage (greenfield)
+- Build cross-book / cross-market detector reusing the recon engine + ledger + `evidence_stats`; run through the *same* shadow → evidence-grade → promotion loop from day one. Do **after** Stage-1 banks capital.
+
+### Q8. Capital governance (once ≥1 lane proven)
+- Portfolio-level fractional-Kelly allocator with per-lane exposure limits + daily cross-lane reconciliation.
